    "LyapunovFunction[a, c] represents the solution of the Lyapunov \
differential equation x' == a . x + x . a^\\[Dagger] + c. LyapunovFunction[a, \
b, c] represents x' == a . x + x . b + c. LyapunovFunction[spec][x0, t] \
returns the value at time t for initial condition x0. \
LyapunovFunction[spec][x0, {t1, t2, ..., tn}] returns a list of values at \
times {t1, t2, ..., tn}.", "synonyms" -> {}, "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> 
